    "text": "Any official communication or public announcement by the Sri Lanka Police is disseminated exclusively through the Police Media Division and released to the media under appropriate headings as formal press releases. In addition, verified updates and public awareness messages are regularly published through the official Facebook page and YouTube channel of the Sri Lanka Police. The Sri Lanka Police has initiated necessary measures to investigate whether the dissemination of such misleading information, falsely presented as an official communication, is a deliberate act carried out by an individual or organized group. The general public is kindly requested to exercise caution, discernment, and responsibility when engaging with or sharing such content. Police Media Division",
